HEADWORD: Miliola
<hw>Mil"i*o`la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., dim. of
L. <ets>milium</ets> millet. So named from its resemblance to millet
seed.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of <ord>Foraminifera</ord>,
having a porcelanous shell with several longitudinal chambers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

